{"tid":375303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華 裔 女 下 跪 向 白 人 男 友 求 婚","createTime":"2017-08-26T12:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T12:51:48.000Z","uid":35964,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08acddec45dead934206ba2a90ea52898980a000","tid":375303,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"美國洛杉磯一名男子為抱得美人歸，特地找人假扮成電影公司為演員兼女友試鏡，期間他現身下跪求婚，女友大為驚喜但尷尬拒絕。不過原來她並非真的拒絕他，而是她早預備戒指向男友求婚，大團圓結局。<br />\n<br />\n波德雷(Brad Podray)哄騙姓宋女友(Hannah Sung)到沙特阿拉伯一間電影公司見工，波德雷戴上黑色臉紗，將自己裝扮成「傳統的穆斯林婦女」演員「Neena」。他又聘請一名演員充當電影製片人，要求女友觀察「Neena」再轉身憑記憶畫下她的外表。<br />\n<br />\n當女友畫完轉身就發現波德雷拿着戒指求婚說：「可否嫁給我？」她當下大為震驚，波德雷走到她跟前單膝下跪，告訴她被整蠱。<br />\n<br />\n女友大叫「我的天」，但尷尬地拒絕：「這不如我所想，對不起。」波德雷看來當場被拒，面上隨即流露失望表情，不過她卻在袋中找呀找，終於拿出戒指，又扶起男友並雙膝跪下問：「可否和我結婚？」<br />\n<br />\n原來女友早已準備戒指兩個月，就是希望等男友求婚時拿出讓自己也求婚，兩人大團圓結局，片段上載後獲網民祝福：「這真棒！我很喜歡，再一次祝福兩人，天生一對。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/66dfda7fef6a7ac314295819676f22cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F66dfda7fef6a7ac314295819676f22cb.png&h=7258ff89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dfede6522537549fdbb15418e9f71750c59620d","tid":375303,"uid":55488,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:01:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5308378ed65eb4d434a0d44be9dcb09a347e1a7d","tid":375303,"uid":62815,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:05:59.000Z","msg":"港男一世都無份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e15ac4ba872cfc4a1c5685924ffbecbbaffa0d2","tid":375303,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:22:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"425e4c851288e64cfdba21c182a82ac1e8ae9c36","tid":375303,"uid":34685,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sr6y7ve9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsr6y7ve9&h=e3e06a54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19c3575a98139aeb5c21ac2db3d51073176892d2","tid":375303,"uid":3801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:45:22.000Z","msg":"等睇人炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966d8a385a3068e0499254e7b0686ba93fbdec22","tid":375303,"uid":75137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:48:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港男一世都無份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黃種男人已經係食物鏈嘅底層<br />\n港男更加係垃圾中嘅垃圾"},{"pid":"b1f8e4251b27e4ec14f4babe25012adefe07bb50","tid":375303,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:51:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等睇人炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n交通黑點🤣"}]}